data.description: Alexis Skyy has the rare distinction of being in multiple series in the Love & Hip Hop franchise. Her latest stop is Love & Hip Hop: Atlanta, where her storyline is set to showcase the artist and reality star opening up about being a sex trafficking victim.
data.title: 'Love & Hip Hop: Atlanta': Alexis Skyy Will Open up About Being a Victim of Sex Trafficking in Season 9
